data.description:
Two separate homes on one parcel!
A duplex main home with a detached accessory dwelling unit (ADU). The duplex upstairs and the ADU are both currently rented. Use this property as an owner occupied, or rent all three. The ADU has a clean foundation, and an unfinished basement that could be finished. This first time public sale property is a perfect example of age only being a number! These homes have been well cared for, and constructed to last. There are many updates throughout, so please ask to see a home features sheet, and view the virtual tour!
